Missions.Title: Defense of the Prodigy IV
Missions.Description: Defeat the attackers. Also, it's your duty to find out more about the unknown ship.

Missions.Title: Pirate ship beaming deck
Missions.Description: Antares III warns you: Those are pirates, selling their prisoners as slaves. Since they got three of your crew members, you decide to pay them a visit and beam up into their ship...

Objectives.Description: Get rid of the cyborg guards!
Find the switch to the bridge.
They will never sit in peace again!

Missions.Title: The bridge
Missions.Description: You enter the bridge. Now it is important to distract the pirates by destroying their stuff. It may help that you found some new weapon: the needler

Missions.Title: The pirate king
Missions.Description: As you enter a room, you hear a voice "You'll never make it alive from my ship!" That's your chance to take out the captain!

Missions.Title: To the rescue
Missions.Description: Get your team members out of there. You already freed two, so that's one to go.

Objectives.Description: Rig their ship by stealing an important device.

Missions.Title: The escape
Missions.Description: It seems, the pirates have realized that they have no chance, so they are trying to go out with you. Get out there fast!

Missions.Title: Xurion pt. 1
Missions.Description: You aren't finished, yet. Two crew members already got sold to Xurian slavers and you must go after them!

Objectives.Description: Better destroy those predator alien pods...

Missions.Title: Xurion pt. 2
Missions.Description: To free your crew members, more information about the terrain is required. Find maps or geospatial data.

Missions.Title: Xurion pt. 3
Missions.Description: You got into the slaver base, but it looks your crew members already freed themselves. Just wipe out the remaining slavers and destroy their weaponry.

Missions.Title: Till you drop
Missions.Description: You have a little party, awaiting shore leave...

Objectives.Description: Your last chance to collect points... err I mean stuff.
